des: Noah Mendlinger reaches on a fielder's choice, fielded by third baseman Justin Guerrera.   Juniel Querecuto scores.    Justin Toerner scores.    Kramer Robertson to 3rd.  Throwing error by third baseman Justin Guerrera.
